Easily find duplicates of network requests.

Just install the extension, open browser devtools and click "RD" tab. Start testing your website and when the extension detect two or more identical requests, it will display them in request list. The tool is useful for QA engineers, developers and other people who care about their computing resources.

Features:
- find request duplicates;
- show start time of each found duplicate;
- filter duplicates by domain, configure time gap and compare requests input data option;
- explore details of requests.

New:
- download daily report of issues;

Please leave your feedback and tell us which feature you need. This will help us make a more powerful extension!
